WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-US

00:00:10.360 --> 00:00:25.520
Put on a non-sterile apron.

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:31.000
Take a brush.

00:00:33.760 --> 00:00:36.340
1. MECHANICAL HAND SCRUB

00:00:36.900 --> 00:00:43.100
Moisten your hands and forearms.

00:00:44.240 --> 00:00:57.180
Prewash your hands and forearms with soap.

00:00:57.940 --> 00:01:05.540
Always start rinsing from your fingertips and proceed towards the elbow.

00:01:08.440 --> 00:01:58.200
Scrub your fingernails, fingers and hands with brush and soap.

00:02:06.200 --> 00:02:25.500
Discard the brush and wash your forearms.

00:02:26.075 --> 00:02:33.315
Again, rinse from fingers to elbows.

00:02:34.720 --> 00:02:38.340
Touch the tap with your elbow only.

00:02:39.273 --> 00:02:41.553
Dry your hands and forearms.

00:02:42.160 --> 00:02:45.640
As with rinsing, proceed from hands towards elbows, never back.

00:02:46.200 --> 00:02:52.660
Use clean towels for the other hand.

00:02:55.700 --> 00:02:58.680
2. HAND DISINFECTION

00:02:59.180 --> 00:03:02.580
Touch the dispenser with your elbow only.

00:03:03.140 --> 00:03:21.500
Rub in the disinfection solution from your fingertips to elbows.

00:03:23.653 --> 00:03:38.053
Rub in the disinfection solution from your fingertips to half of your forearms.

00:03:40.780 --> 00:04:09.080
Rub in the disinfection solution to your fingertips, fingers and hands.

